===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To [[regard]] someone with [[respect]]
#: '''''Esteem''' your elders, boy.''
# to regard something as [[valuable]]; to [[prize]]
# to look upon something in a [[particular]] way
#: ''Mary is an '''esteemed''' member of the community''
